[I] Task Scheduler

[T] KTimer is a little tool to execute programs after some time. It allows you
[T] to enter several tasks and to set a timer for each of them. The timers for
[T] each task can be started, stopped, changed, or looped.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/ktimer/

[A] The KDE-Team
